game.name: Gun Masters
game.description:
Forget all the things and be prepared to get you introduced to the amazing action-packed game where timing is a key to clear all levels! We have brought you today to a brand new shooting game “Gun Masters” in which you have to play the role of a sharp shooter who can defeat all of your opponents with ease. Grab your weapons and get ready to show the world that you are truly the strongest shooter in the neighbourhood! Challenge your shooting skills and clear all levels without dying!
Your enemies also have expertise in shooting, so do not take them easily and try to aim your target accurately before they do the same with you. Do not forget to collect money and purchase new weapons in the shop available for you! It is up to you whether you want to choose the open rare or epic weapons. Your enemies will use all the tricks to stop you from moving forward in this heated html5 combat game. Kill all of them along with their bosses to clear each level!
Do not let the smell of gunpowder burn your lungs and try to keep going on no matter whatever the situation arises in the game! Shoot your enemy with the left mouse button once you see your gun pointing at your enemy! Take your time before shooting as your enemy has the skill to kill you in a single shot! Aiming for the headshots of your enemies will surely help you gain extra points in this one of the best free gun games for boys! Check out more shooting games online to play here without a need of downloading apps!
